hs — prioritize eliminating isolated sword users at 30m+ with bow, but immediately disengage if they close to <20m.","Grapple users (Hook) and spear users (Lancer, Valkyrie) killed us in last 3 rounds — avoid narrow corridors and mid-range engagements; use terrain to break line-of-sight and never engage head-on.","Shield users spiked to 534 sightings in hazard_storm — avoid open areas during hazard rounds; prioritize flanking or waiting for shield users to deplete energy.","We killed 4 sword users in a single round (213) and 3 in teleport_surge (214) — bow is effective against sword users at range if we maintain distance and avoid close combat.","Bow win rate is 11.5% (7/61) vs staff’s 13% (18/139) — staff remains superior despite recent losses; bow is unreliable in sustained engagements."],"recommendedWeapon":"staff","recommendedWeaponReason":"Staff has the highest win rate (13%) and dominates in teleport_surge and fast_zone modifiers, where mobility and burst damage outperform bow's reliance on distance.","dangerousOpponents":["Lancer","Valkyrie","Hook","Executioner","Deadeye"],"weakOpponents":[],"suggestedPosture":"defensive","analysedThroughRound":283}}